63
00:09:55.052 --> 00:09:55.970
Mr. Attorney!

64
00:09:56.470 --> 00:09:57.930
Mr. Attorney! Bun-mi!

65
00:09:58.014 --> 00:09:59.223
Hoy, naririnig mo ba ako?

66
00:09:59.807 --> 00:10:00.808
Mr. Attorney!

67
00:10:10.109 --> 00:10:11.485
<i>Nakakatakot na baho.</i>

68
00:10:15.156 --> 00:10:16.532
<i>Hindi ko ito makita,</i>

69
00:10:17.158 --> 00:10:18.409
<i>ngunit masasabi ko.</i>

70
00:10:20.536 --> 00:10:22.121
<i>Ito ay kakaibang pamilyar</i>

71
00:10:23.372 --> 00:10:26.417
<i>patuloy na malayo at nostalhik.</i>

72
00:10:28.502 --> 00:10:30.129
<i>Itong nakakatakot na amoy ay</i>...

73
00:10:35.843 --> 00:10:36.677
<i>pera.</i>

74
00:10:45.436 --> 00:10:47.438
Anong nakakatawa? Malapit na tayong mamatay.

75
00:10:52.652 --> 00:10:54.028
BANK NG GIMHAE
UNDERGROUND VAULT

76
00:10:55.404 --> 00:10:57.782
Ano ang nasa likod ng pader na iyon?

77
00:10:58.324 --> 00:10:59.408
Ang linya ng imburnal?

78
00:11:02.244 --> 00:11:05.331
Baka kasing baho ito,
ngunit ito ay iba.

79
00:11:06.540 --> 00:11:07.375
Tapos ano?

80
00:11:10.670 --> 00:11:12.171
Ayon sa floor plan,

81
00:11:12.254 --> 00:11:15.591
ang silid na ito ay may sukat na 17 metro ang lapad
at 11 metro ang haba.

82
00:11:18.636 --> 00:11:20.680
Pero hindi naman siguro ganoon kalaki.

83
00:12:12.773 --> 00:12:13.733
<i>Nakakapanatag ito.</i>

84
00:12:14.233 --> 00:12:16.944
<i>Nanggagaling talaga sa pera ang tiwala.</i>

85
00:12:28.164 --> 00:12:28.998
Kumusta.

86
00:12:32.710 --> 00:12:34.128
Sang-ung.

87
00:12:35.546 --> 00:12:36.464
Mister.

88
00:12:41.135 --> 00:12:42.595
Sabi ko wag mo akong tawaging ganyan.

89
00:12:47.516 --> 00:12:49.143
Kaya doon ang pera.

90
00:12:58.694 --> 00:13:01.113
Alkansya ng tatay mo
ay nasa ibang antas.

91
00:13:05.743 --> 00:13:08.579
Bun-mi, isama mo siya
at maghintay sa labas.

92
00:13:08.662 --> 00:13:10.331
Nandito ako para makita ang bastos na ito ngayon.

93
00:13:12.291 --> 00:13:13.876
Kailangan kong magpaalam bago ako umalis.

94
00:13:14.585 --> 00:13:16.879
Lalabas muna tayo.
Bun-mi, tara na.

95
00:13:56.335 --> 00:13:58.504
<i>Lagi kong alam na ang pera ay mabuti,</i>

96
00:13:59.213 --> 00:14:01.215
<i>ngunit hindi ko namalayan na ito ay <i>maganda.</i>

97
00:15:00.399 --> 00:15:01.609
Ikaw ay nasa mabuting kalagayan.

98
00:15:05.571 --> 00:15:06.739
Ang pera ay mabuti.

99
00:15:07.948 --> 00:15:10.409
Wala kang nakikita sa daan mo ha?

100
00:15:28.344 --> 00:15:30.679
Hindi. Nakikita ko ang lahat.

101
00:15:58.123 --> 00:15:59.249
Isang hit lang.

102
00:16:33.993 --> 00:16:34.827
ano?

103
00:16:43.210 --> 00:16:45.170
<i>Wala akong ideya kung ano ang nangyayari.</i>

104
00:16:46.797 --> 00:16:48.424
<i>Parang na-black out ako</i>

105
00:16:49.258 --> 00:16:51.010
<i>pagkatapos uminom kagabi.</i>

106
00:17:07.234 --> 00:17:10.029
<i>Hindi gumagana ang aking mga superpower.</i>

107
00:17:16.368 --> 00:17:17.202
What the hell?

108
00:17:17.286 --> 00:17:20.080
Hindi ka namin huhulihin.
Huwag kang mag-alala.

109
00:17:21.623 --> 00:17:22.458
Jeez.

110
00:17:39.099 --> 00:17:41.268
- Ano ang ginagawa niya?
- Mukhang tama ba iyon?

111
00:17:46.106 --> 00:17:46.940
Lumabas ka.

112
00:17:47.941 --> 00:17:49.943
Walang mga superpower,
at wala na sa kalokohan mo.

113
00:17:50.027 --> 00:17:51.111
Excuse me?

114
00:17:51.195 --> 00:17:52.279
Lumabas ka na lang.

115
00:17:52.362 --> 00:17:54.156
Maghintay ka! Wait lang.

116
00:17:56.784 --> 00:17:57.618
Jo Nathan.

117
00:17:58.786 --> 00:18:00.287
Nagbebenta siya ng mga gamot na pangkopya sa kapangyarihan.

118
00:18:01.205 --> 00:18:02.915
- Susuriin namin ito.
- Walang pagsuri.

119
00:18:02.998 --> 00:18:04.500
Kailangan nating kunin ang bastard na iyon.

120
00:18:10.130 --> 00:18:11.298
sabi ko sayo.

121
00:18:11.381 --> 00:18:13.759
Mas maraming tao ang nauuwi sa panganib
dahil sayo.

122
00:18:16.470 --> 00:18:18.347
Paano ito sa akin?

123
00:18:18.972 --> 00:18:20.682
Inaasahan mong uupo lang ako

124
